des:
WATASHI IoT products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off your plug.
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your plug - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.
After connecting Alexa to your WATASHI IoT products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "WATASHI IoT" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register an account in our "WATASHI IoT" app;
(3). You need to have some WATASHI IoT devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "WATASHI IoT" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "WATASHI IoT" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "WATASHI IoT" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "WATASHI IoT", and you'll be navigated to "WATASHI IoT" login page;
(9). Open "WATASHI IoT" App, click More Service, choose "Alexa". Link with Verification Code, copy the Code, put code into the login page；
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the plug.”
“Alexa, turn off the plug.”
